headline: CSX downgraded to Hold from Buy at Loop Capital
summary: Loop Capital analyst Rick Paterson downgraded CSX (CSX) to Hold from Buy with a price target of $34, down from $40, as part of a broader research note downgrading the Transportation sector based on the announcement of Canada tariffs by the White House.
